message.text:
𝑫𝒂𝒌𝒂𝒍 𝑨 𝑺𝒂𝒍𝒂𝒎𝒂𝒕, 𝒀'𝒆𝒓𝒔! 🪁🧡

Dahil sa inyo, we proved that there are no limits in our skies. ☁️🍃

From Tamaraw’s Choice for Best Poster to becoming 500 leaders stronger. 🏆 Truly, every milestone is possible because of you. 🎉

The FEU College Y Club stands proud as the 𝑯𝒐𝒎𝒆 𝒐𝒇 𝑪𝒐𝒏𝒔𝒊𝒔𝒕𝒆𝒏𝒕 𝑳𝒆𝒂𝒅𝒆𝒓𝒔 and the 𝑷𝒓𝒆𝒎𝒊𝒆𝒓 𝑺𝒕𝒖𝒅𝒆𝒏𝒕 𝑳𝒆𝒂𝒅𝒆𝒓𝒔𝒉𝒊𝒑 𝑶𝒓𝒈𝒂𝒏𝒊𝒛𝒂𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏 𝒐𝒇 𝑭𝑬𝑼 𝑴𝒂𝒏𝒊𝒍𝒂. Together, we continue to grow, inspire, and defy limits. 😉🫵

This is only the beginning, Y'ers. With you by our side, mas marami pa tayong sabay-sabay na mararating. 🙌

#CYCibolSaHimPAMPawid
#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27
#TamHunt2025

Publication Material by Ciara Predas

message.text:
𝑫𝒂𝒌𝒂𝒍 𝑨 𝑺𝒂𝒍𝒂𝒎𝒂𝒕, 𝒀'𝒆𝒓𝒔! 🪁🧡

Dahil sa inyo, we proved that there are no limits in our skies. ☁️🍃

From Tamaraw’s Choice for Best Poster to becoming 500 leaders stronger. 🏆 Truly, every milestone is possible because of you. 🎉

This is only the beginning, Y'ers. With you by our side, mas marami pa tayong sabay-sabay na mararating. 🙌

#CYCibolSaHimPAMPawid
#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27
#TamHunt2025
